<p>
<lb n="1"/>ṣa dēva<unclear>rgga</unclear>valliya <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>vājaśanēyariṁnūrvvargge tamma prabhu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>tvada guḍḍa mānyadoḷagippattēḷu gēṇa
<lb n="4" break="no"/>bandhucintāmaṇiya kōlalaṟuva
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ttu mattarkkeyyamanondu mattarttō
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṭamumaṁ śāleya suttaluṁ nā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>lkuṁ bīdiyiṁdoḷaguḷḷa maneya
<lb n="8" break="no"/>nivēśanaṁgaḷmaṁ bandhucintāmaṇiya
<lb n="9"/>hastada mūvattukaynīḷada hanni
<lb n="10" break="no"/>kaiyyagalada baṇaṁbeya nivēśana
<lb n="11" break="no"/>mumaṁ ta(ṁ)mmaṁśake banderaḍuppinakaṭṭe
<lb n="12" break="no"/>yumanavaṟa bennikegaṭṭe
<lb n="13" break="no"/>yumaṁ dhārāpūrvvakaṁ mā
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ḍi koṭṭaru niviṣṭargge Ī dharmmamaṁ
<lb n="15"/>pratipāḷisidavaru sahaśrā
<lb n="16" break="no"/>śvamēdhaphalamaṁ paḍevaru <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

